The '''Dusky Sky Café''' was a restaurant located in the city of [[Cambriele]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ralltiir/Legends|Ralltiir]] during the years following the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]]. The Dusky Sky was owned and operated by an [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorian]] named [[Kikow]].

